text:
Our friends at @JohnsHopkins have unleashed their new COVID tracker today.
Unbelievably impressive. Gives county-by-county view of everything, not just cases&fatality rates, but insurance & poverty rates, racial breakdown, much more--all on a county level. https://t.co/oTED531HQu
